# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:3
translate chinese u20l_c0cbad5f:

    # "For now, I should go see Brandi."
    "现在，我得去见布兰迪。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:6
translate chinese u20l_6783b0e6:

    # "I drive to Brandi's apartment and knock on her door."
    "我开车去布兰迪的公寓，敲了敲她的门。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:7
translate chinese u20l_7043290e:

    # "It's late, but I hope she'll still be awake. I have to see her."
    "虽然很晚了，但我希望她还没睡。我必须见她。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:11
translate chinese u20l_1ccac3d3:

    # "After a few moments, Brandi opens the door."
    "过了一会儿，布兰迪打开了门。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:12
translate chinese u20l_4a243063:

    # fd "Holy shit, [pcname]! You're back!"
    fd "天啊，[pcname]！你回来了！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:15
translate chinese u20l_ad7d3606:

    # "I wrap my arms around Brandi, pulling her in tight."
    "我搂住布兰迪，紧紧地把她抱在怀里。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:16
translate chinese u20l_e1a3df9c:

    # fd "I thought that machine killed you!"
    fd "我还以为那台机器把你给害死了！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:17
translate chinese u20l_ebe2f7cf:

    # fd "I thought I was never going to see you again!"
    fd "我还以为再也见不到你了！"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:20
translate chinese u20l_946b2987:

    # fd "What happened to you? Did you really go to another world, like you said?"
    fd "你到底怎么了？你真的像你说的那样去了另一个世界吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:21
translate chinese u20l_aac4f177:

    # pc "Yeah, I did. I saw my dad again. It was... a lot."
    pc "是的，我去了。我又见到了我爸爸。那……太震撼了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:22
translate chinese u20l_34a96f57:

    # fd "Wow, I can't believe it. Are you okay?"
    fd "哇，真不敢相信。你没事吧？"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:23
translate chinese u20l_3c3fa8e3:

    # pc "Yeah, I'm great. I'll tell you everything tomorrow, I promise."
    pc "嗯，我很好。明天我全都告诉你，我保证。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:26
translate chinese u20l_4188b1fa:

    # fd "I'm just so glad you're back."
    fd "我只是太高兴你能回来了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:27
translate chinese u20l_80452f29:

    # fd "You're going to have to cut that hair though. Big oof."
    fd "不过你得把头发剪短了。天哪，太长了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:30
translate chinese u20l_7d64063d:

    # "She kisses me softly, her lips warm and inviting."
    "她轻轻吻了我，双唇温暖而诱人。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:31
translate chinese u20l_392f9f2c:

    # fd "I'm so happy you came home."
    fd "你回家了，我太开心了。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20l.rpy:32
translate chinese u20l_4d7d812c:

    # fd "Let's get you in the shower. You smell like a horse."
    fd "快去冲个澡吧。你身上有股马的味道。"

